      "text": "Bring my soul out of prison, That I may give thanks unto thy name: The righteous shall compass me about; For thou wilt deal bountifully with me.",
      "versionTitle": "American Standard Version"
    },
    {
      "language": "en",
      "ref": "Psalm 142:7",
